author: COMSOL
description:
This example demonstrates the Single Particle Battery interface for studying the discharge of a lithium-ion battery. The model is isothermal and is set in 0D. The single particle formulation is typically valid for low-medium current scenarios.

The results for different discharge currents are compared against a more extended 1D formulation of a lithium ion-battery (li_battery_1d).
